cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a deep 3D convolutional neural network for Alzheimer's disease diagnosis based on brain images. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) as it involves image analysis and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) as it uses deep learning techniques. The paper also mentions pre-training the network, which falls under neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the experiments involve the use of MRI scans, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
